These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: hip-hop, disco
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the fan of disco##1
2. the fan of disco is not to the right of the fan of disco##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2  |
| Music-Genre   | disco | hip-hop |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: romance, comedy
1. the person watching romance movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching romance movies is not to the left of the person watching comedy movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | romance |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-3::.
2 different pets are kept: cat, hamster
1. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hamster##5
2. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
3. the owner of the cat is not to the right of the owner of the cat##8

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |    2     |
| Pet   | cat | hamster |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-4::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: subway, bus
1. the person driving the subway is not to the right of the person driving the subway##8
2. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2   |
| Transport   | subway | bus |

 #################################

 
